bilingual.target: 所以我给她买了一辆自行车。

bilingual.source: Do you have any bicycle rental apps?
bilingual.target: 你有任何自行车租赁应用吗？

bilingual.source: Hello, Emma! I have a new bicycle.
bilingual.target: 你好，艾玛！我有一辆新自行车。

bilingual.source: Or riding my bicycle, wheels going round?
bilingual.target: 还是骑我的自行车，轮子转动？

bilingual.source: My sister said, "Please buy me a bicycle."
bilingual.target: 我妹妹说：“请给我买辆自行车。”

bilingual.source: Jimmy fixes up broken bicycle parts, like wheels.
bilingual.target: 吉米修理破损的自行车零件，比如车轮。

bilingual.source: Johannes, an elderly person, fell off his bicycle last night.
bilingual.target: 约翰内斯，一位老人，昨晚从自行车上摔下来。

list.abstract: bicycle，英语单词。作名词为自行车；脚踏车。作动词为骑自行车。例句：He designed a shining bicycle path.（他设计了一条闪闪发光的自行车道）。 近义词有bike、cycle、pushbike。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig is going to ride on Peppa's little bicycle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爸爸要骑佩佩的小自行车了。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig is going to ride on Peppa's little bicycle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爸爸要骑佩佩的小自行车了。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa has her bicycle. George has his tricycle. Mummy and Daddy have their tandem.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇有自行车，乔治也有自行车，爸爸妈妈有双人自行车。

yingyinNormal.en: Is the woman on the bicycle still alive? Yeah, she jumped right back up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自行车上的老太太还活着吗？活着！她及时跳开了！

yingyinNormal.en: Three clocks are much better than one. Dad, have you got a bicycle bell, please?
yingyinNormal.zh: 三个时钟可比一个好多了。爸爸，可不可以给我已给自行车铃呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Three clocks are much better than one. Dad, have you got a bicycle bell, please?
yingyinNormal.zh: 三个时钟可比一个好多了。爸爸，可不可以给我已给自行车铃呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa wishes she did not have stabilizers on her bicycle. Daddy, I don't want stabilizers anymore. Do you think you can ride without them? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩琪现在希望自己的自行车上没有辅助轮。爸爸，我不想再自行车上装辅助轮了。你没有它们能骑好吗？是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Alright, Peppa. Let's take them off. Daddy Pig is taking the stabilizers off Peppa's bicycle. Are you sure you want to ride without stabilizers? Yes!
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的，佩琪，那就把它们拆掉。猪爸爸把自行车后面的辅助轮拆掉了。你确定你骑自行车时 可以不用辅助轮？是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Freddy Fox now has two bicycle bells. Brilliant. Thanks, dad. Dad gave me two bells.
yingyinNormal.zh: 狐狸弗雷迪现在有两个自行车铃。太棒了，谢谢你爸爸。爸爸给了我两个车铃。

yingyinNormal.en: Freddy Fox now has two bicycle bells. Brilliant. Thanks, Dad. Dad gave me two bells.
yingyinNormal.zh: 狐狸弗雷迪现在有两个自行车铃。太棒了，谢谢你爸爸。爸爸给了我两个车铃。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig is riding Peppa's little bicycle. Have a nice ride to work. I will, Peppa. Bye. Bye.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爸爸骑上了佩奇的小自行车，祝你工作愉快爸爸。我会的，佩奇，再见！再见！

yingyinNormal.en: That's nothing. I couldn't ride a bicycle 'cause my mother was afraid I'd hit a bump and lose my virginity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这没什么，我妈不让我骑自行车因为她怕我撞到什么，从此不再是处女身。

yingyinNormal.en: What shall we play now? Let's have a bicycle race. With a big, shiny cup for the winner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们现在该玩什么呢。我们来比赛骑自行车怎么样。赢了的人就可以得到一个亮闪闪的大奖杯。

yingyinNormal.en: What shall we play now? Let's have a bicycle race. With a big, shiny cup for the winner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们现在该玩什么呢？我们来比赛骑自行车怎么样。赢了的人就可以得到一个亮闪闪的大奖杯。

yingyinNormal.en: It's impossible. It takes time to learn how to do important things like riding a bicycle or playing the piano.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个根本就不可能！重要的事需要花时间才能学会比如说骑自行车或者是弹钢琴。

yingyinNormal.en: I am winning. It is not a race, Peppa. It's just a gentle bicycle ride. Yes, Daddy but I'm still winning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我比你们快。我们没有在比赛，佩奇，这是场轻松的自行车之类。是的，爸爸，但是我比较快。

yingyinNormal.en: You've got to get fit somehow. I know. You can use my bicycle. Yes, and then you'll get some fresh air as well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你必须通过某种方法来保持健康。我知道.你可以用我的自行车。是的，然后你还可以呼吸一些新鲜空气。

yingyinNormal.en: You've got to get fit somehow. I know. You can use my bicycle. Yes, and then you'll get some fresh air as well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你必须通过某种方法来保持健康。我知道.你可以用我的自行车。是的，然后你还可以呼吸一些新鲜空气。

yingyinNormal.en: The best thing about having your own cement mixer is... Dad, have you got a big shiny winner's cup for our bicycle race, please?
yingyinNormal.zh: 自己拥有一台水泥搅拌机的好处就是... 爸爸，能给我们的自行车比赛找一个。亮闪闪的大奖杯吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: They can also learn geometry by assembling a <highlight>bicycle</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们还可以通过组装自行车来学习几何学。

examination_example.sentence: Princes and princesses have day-jobs and ride <highlight>bicycles</highlight>, not horses (or helicopters).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 王子和公主们白天骑自行车去工作，而不是骑马（也不是乘坐直升机）。
